Author: olamidey
Title: [ANN] CryptoBike (CBS) - A Currency Powering The Bike Sharing Economy
Body: Having an automated bike sharing system seems like a perfect system, where payments would be perfected with a single currency, I believe that's exactly what cryptobike is all about, trying to seize the opportunity of Blockchain technology to create a currency that will facilitate the bike sharing system. Lots of people are loving this vision with evidence of their social media followers,  the team seems to be up to the task as well as its road map. The best part about cryptobike is it is unique.
